data.description: We are bringing in the new year with this new listing! This colonial brick style home has everything your family needs including a fifth room on the first floor that could be used as a bedroom, office, or study. The sunroom is great for morning coffee breaks or settling down with a nice book.  The laundry room has plenty of space to sort and fold laundry including a wash basin, a long counter, and cabinets for storage. There is a full bathroom on each floor and all bedrooms are a decent size. HVAC, Roof, and Hot Water Heater all replaced within the last 5 years. All this home needs is your personal touch. Come check it out today!
